title: Good Times - Celebrating 50 Years of Alberts Productions
description:
This massive five disc collection offers 102 tracks from the Alberts label. Spanning 50 years from 1964 til now, you'll hear songs from many Australian artists, including Billy Thorpe and the Aztecs, The Easybeats, Ted Mulry Gang, Stevie Wright, Flash and the Pan, the Angels, Rose Tattoo, John Paul Young, and AC/DC!

In lossless FLAC format (seperate tracks) with Replay Gain metadata included.
